#. REF: pts-cs60, sc60
msgctxt "dn29:60.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā upavāṇo bhagavato piṭṭhito ṭhito hoti bhagavantaṃ bījayamāno. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Upavāṇa was standing behind the Buddha fanning him. "

msgctxt "dn29:60.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā upavāṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "He said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "dn29:60.3"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing! "

msgctxt "dn29:60.4"
msgid "Pāsādiko vatāyaṃ, bhante, dhammapariyāyo; "
msgstr "This exposition of the teaching is impressive, sir, "

msgctxt "dn29:60.5"
msgid "supāsādiko vatāyaṃ, bhante, dhammapariyāyo, ko nāmāyaṃ, bhante, dhammapariyāyo”ti? "
msgstr "it is very impressive. Sir, what is the name of this exposition of the teaching?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn29:60.6"
msgid "“Tasmātiha tvaṃ, upavāṇa, imaṃ dhammapariyāyaṃ ‘pāsādiko’ tveva naṃ dhārehī”ti. "
msgstr "“Well, Upavāṇa, you may remember this exposition of the teaching as ‘The Impressive Discourse’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs61, sc61
msgctxt "dn29:61.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "dn29:61.2"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā upavāṇo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Upavāṇa was happy with what the Buddha said. "

